This application contains three files as
1. main.c
2. helper.c
3. header.h
we can compile this application as 
gcc main.c helper.c -o final

After this command final named executable file gets created then we can runthis file as
./final

To perform this above task we can create makefile and write the above command in that file as it is.
all is the target in this makefile.

we can use command as make which run our makefile.
